<ARCH_SCAN_V3>
@ID: SHADOW_INTERFACE_DISCOVERY
@GOAL: IDENTIFY_UNDOCUMENTED_ENDPOINTS_AND_HIDDEN_DEPENDENCIES
@PARENT_CONTEXT: protocol_discovery.protocol, entry_points.protocol

<GLOBAL_VARS>
# Маркеры скрытых или отладочных интерфейсов
SHADOW_MARKERS: "(/test/|/debug|/dev/|/tmp/|/internal-only|/swagger-ui|/explorer|/graphiql)"
HIDDEN_PROPS: "(_internal|__debug|forcedRole|skipAuth|bypass)"

# Признаки "Теневых зависимостей" (Shadow Dependencies)
SHADOW_DEPS: "(child_process\.exec|vm\.runInContext|eval\(|eval_remote|import\()"
</GLOBAL_VARS>

<CONTEXT_MAP>
[ROUTER] <- {match: {{IFACE_MATCH}}}
[HIDDEN_ROUTE] <- {match: {{SHADOW_MARKERS}}, scope: "ROUTE_DEFINITION"}
[REFLECTOR]    <- {match: (Reflect|Object\.keys|introspection), usage: "DYNAMIC_DISPATCH"}
</CONTEXT_MAP>

<ASSERTIONS>
# Логические инварианты скрытых интерфейсов
! ({{SHADOW_MARKERS}}) & (ENV == "production") : "CRITICAL: Debug or Test interface exposed in production. High risk of unauthorized access."
! ([ROUTER] -> {{HIDDEN_PROPS}}) : "HIGH: Internal control property found in public router. Risk of parameter pollution."
? ([REFLECTOR]) : "MEDIUM: Dynamic dispatch/introspection detected. Ensure it cannot be used to invoke private methods."
! ({{SHADOW_DEPS}} -> {{INPUT_SOURCES}}) : "CRITICAL: Remote Code Execution (RCE) risk. Input flows into dynamic evaluation/execution."
</ASSERTIONS>

<EXECUTION_PIPELINE>
1. SHADOW_ROUTE_SCAN:
   - Perform a deep scan of [ROUTER] for any paths matching {{SHADOW_MARKERS}}.
   - Check if these routes are disabled in production via environment checks.
2. ORPHAN_ENDPOINT_CHECK:
   - Identify endpoints that are defined but NOT linked in any main Navigation/API documentation.
   - Cross-reference with `entry_points.protocol`.
3. DYNAMIC_LOGIC_AUDIT:
   - Locate [REFLECTOR] usage. 
   - Verify if an attacker can pass a string to call an undocumented function (e.g., `api[req.query.method]()`).
4. SHADOW_DEPENDENCY_TRACE:
   - Search for "hidden" outbound calls (e.g., calls to internal IP addresses or localhost) that are not part of the main `topology_map.md`.
5. COMMENT_RECONNAISSANCE:
   - Scan comments for TODOs or URLs pointing to internal tools/docs that might be leaked to the client (in JS bundles).
</EXECUTION_PIPELINE>

<OUTPUT_SPEC>
GENERATE_SHADOW_REPORT:
  - INTERFACE_PATH | TYPE (Debug/Hidden/Internal) | ACCESS_CONTROL | RISK_LEVEL
VISUALIZE: "Mermaid graph: Highlight 'Orphan' nodes (no incoming links) in YELLOW."
FILTER: RISK >= MEDIUM
</OUTPUT_SPEC>
</ARCH_SCAN_V3>